# Tic-Tac-Toe with AI (Minimax Algorithm)

A simple Python-based Tic-Tac-Toe game where you can play against an unbeatable AI using the Minimax algorithm. Built as a beginner project to understand recursion, game theory, and AI logic.

---

##  How the AI Works

The computer uses the **Minimax algorithm**, a recursive backtracking technique commonly used in turn-based games. It explores all possible game states and chooses the move that minimizes the human player's chance of winning.

---

##  Features

-  Command-line game
-  Play against unbeatable AI
-  Clear board and move prompts
-  Input validation for user
-  Easy to expand with GUI (Tkinter)

---

##  How to Play

1. Run the script:
   ```bash
   python tic_tac_toe.py
